Raw FASTQ Files
        ↓
Quality Control (FastQC)
        ↓
Reference Alignment (bwa mem)
        ↓
SAM/BAM Processing (samtools)
        ↓
Duplicate Marking
        ↓
Read Group Assignment (GATK)
        ↓
Variant Calling (HaplotypeCaller)
        ↓
Variant Annotation (snpEff / SnpSift)
        ↓
Structural Variant Calling (Manta)
        ↓
Summary Tables & Downstream Analysis
